class ClaudeCodeAdapter <<struct>> {
}

note bottom of ClaudeCodeAdapter
  <b>Hooks delegate to:</b>
  • statusline::parse_statusline
  • transcript::validate_transcript_path
  • transcript::start_tailing
  • test_runners (via transcript)

  <b>JSON parsing is Claude-private</b>
  (domain helpers like `bash_command(item)`,
  `total_input_tokens(value)`, plus small
  Claude-private path helpers for repeated
  3+ deep reads). No shared adapter::json
  module — see decision record at
  docs/decisions/2026-05-03-claude-parser-
  json-boundary.md.
end note

class NoOpAdapter <<struct>> {
  -agent_type: AgentType
  +new(t: AgentType) : Self
}

note bottom of NoOpAdapter
  <b>Stage 1 fallback</b> for Codex /
  Aider / Generic. status_source
  returns Claude's path so the
  watcher's start_for runs as
  today's silent no-op (no events,
  but exit-collapse works in the UI).
  Stage 2 replaces the Codex arm
  of `for_type` with `CodexAdapter`.
end note

